dc_description_s: The Urban Reserve data set shows areas reserved for future development, as specified in the comprehensive plan.Urban reserve areas are outside of and adjacent to UGAs, and reserve a potential supply of urban land for mixed use and employment land uses. More information is available in the General Policy Plan (GPP).Derivative data is routinely refreshed as the master data set is updated.
